We have many internal environments and people also often have many accounts, please double check if you are logged into the right account, if needed use an incognito window if you have multiple accounts logged into AI Hub at the same time. This feature is not released. We are not going to spend much time improving the gating system to address the multiple env / account problem since it's not relevant to external users, so we just need to ask people to be careful and use incognito window if you have that situation -- if anyone is able to see these features without any of these flags turned on in an incognito window please let me know, but I'm pretty confident it is not released.
